          </a>

          <div class="listing__item__content">
            <h3 class="headingIcon icon standard-page">
              <a href="https://www.nationalparks.nsw.gov.au/about-npws/sustainable-tourism" class="">Sustainable tourism and visitation<i class="iea"></i></a>
            </h3>
            <p>Our national parks are important places for conservation and the community. NSW National Parks and Wildlife Service (NPWS) is committed to providing park experiences that support local communities, and conserve our cultural and natural heritage. Many of our tour providers are ECO-certified by <a target="_blank" href="http://www.ecotourism.org.au/our-certification-programs/eco-certification/" class="new-window external">Ecotourism Australia<i class="iea"></i></a> and can be found on the <a href="http://www.ecotourism.org.au/eco-experiences/green-travel-guide/?sStates=NSW&amp;sCertificationDetailPages=&amp;sExperienceTypes=19-15-2-18-3-1-4-5-9-10-11-12-13-14-16-17-20-21-22&amp;sSearchKey=#mapContents" target="_blank" class="new-window external">Green Travel Guide.<i class="iea"></i></a> Look for the NSW National Parks logo on this website.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
